{
  "stem": "17001.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 162.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean, this was the custom, the real European custom, not the American.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In America, they do it only in Borough Park and Williamsburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother had a very, very good friend whom she went to school together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And her children were very good friend with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, we had-- we had I would say mostly Jewish friend, because somehow, the non-Jews, they didn't want-- they didn't associate themselves with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on, when they became like teenagers, in the age of let's say 16, 17, then they would go to dancing school together and they became friends.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But as children, you-- you didn't associate too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The school was a very nice general elementary school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were six grade in one building, one room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes I think about that, how amazing it is that one teacher was able to teach six grade in the same classroom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were no turmoil and there were no interference and each one learned the ABC and each one learned how to read.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when it was the time that we were like in third grade, fourth grade, you had to stand back to the map with a stick showing when he asked where is this state, where is that state, where is this river, where is that river.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometimes it amazes me to-- to put you through such a drill.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after that, I went to the middle school, the gymnasium, which was far away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to take a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The train station was very far away from our home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And during the winter, sometimes the snow drifts were so big I fell into it and I thought I'd never climb out of it, but I did.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
